GAMEPAD 1:
A: Shoot One
X: Shoot All Macro
Y: Toggle Shooter
B: Reset Spindex Macro
Down: Toggle Speed
Left: One Ball Left
Up: Toggle LockOn
Right: One Ball Right
LeftBump: Spin In
RightBump: Spin Out
LeftTrig: Turret Manual Left
RightTrig: Turret Manual Right
LStX: Strafe
LStY: Movement
RStX: Turning
RStY: Turning
LStCl:
RStCl:
Back:
Start:


GAMEPAD 2:
A: Hood Offset Down 0.05
X: EmptyBalls
Y: Hood Offset Up 0.05
B: Override Lock
Down: RPM Offset Down 50
Left: Spindexer Left Manual
Up: RPM Offset Up 50
Right: Spindexer Right Manual
LeftBump: Switch Alliance States
RightBump: Switch Motif States
LeftTrig: Turret Manual Left
RightTrig: Turret Manual Right
LStX:
LStY:
RStX:
RStY:
LStCl: Reset Spindexer
RStCl: Break from state machine
Back:
Start:
